            <div class='col-xs-12 col-sm-12' style="">
                <h4>
                    Install the Gridcoin client
                </h4>
                <h5>
                    Microsoft Windows
                </h5>
                <ul style="text-align: justify; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                        <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="http://download.gridcoin.us/download/downloadstake/GridcoinResearch.msi">Download Windows Client</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
                <h5>
                    macOS
                </h5>
                <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="http://wiki.gridcoin.us/OS_X_Guide">Wiki macOS guide</a>
                <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="https://cryptocointalk.com/topic/13139-os-x-builds-feedback-bug-reporting/">macOS Build Support thread</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
                <h5>
                    Debian Packages (Ubuntu)
                </h5>
                <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="https://code.launchpad.net/~gridcoin/+archive/ubuntu/gridcoin-stable">Launchpad built ubuntu releases</a>
                <ul>
                    <li>sudo add-apt-repository ppa:gridcoin/gridcoin-stable</li>
                    <li>sudo apt-get update</li>
                    <li>sudo apt-get install gridcoinresearchd</li>
                    <li>gridcoinresearchd</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
                <h5>
                    RPM Packages (Opensuse/Fedora)
                </h5>
                <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="https://build.opensuse.org/package/show/home:theMarix/gridcoin">OpenSuse/Fedora RPMs</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
                <h5>
                    AUR (Archlinux)
                </h5>
                <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/gridcoinresearch-qt">Archlinux AUR package</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
                <h5>
                    Manually compile the Gridcoin client
                </h5>
                <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="http://wiki.gridcoin.us/Linux_guide">Linux compiling guide</a>
                <a class="btn btn-simple btn-default" style="margin:5px;" href="https://github.com/gridcoin/Gridcoin-Research">Gridcoin GitHub Repo</a>
                <h4>
                    Initial client setup
                </h4>
                    <p>
                        Once the client launches, a prompt will request an email address - do not enter an email address, rather click the 'Cancel' button and proceed past any additional prompts.
                    </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
